ActPublic Service Labour Relations Act
SubjectNFB-CUPE - Operational and Administrative Support categories ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the renewal of the COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT between the NATIONAL FILM BOARD AND THE CANADIAN UNION OF PUBLIC EMPLOYEES regarding the Operational and the Administrative support categories. This agreement is for a term of three (3) years from July 1, 2011 to June 30, 2014.
